Articles.Content:
WARSAW-ONE is a Polish Deepspace exploration vessel, It's main purpose is to explore the Gas-Giants. It's current assignment is to explore the Sarnus system and investigate the rings. It will later visit Jool.

![K6kAjuy.png](http://i.imgur.com/K6kAjuy.png)

**WARSAW-ONE Sling shotting itself around Slate to be intercepted in to a Sarnus orbit.**

![IlRCFXt.png](http://i.imgur.com/IlRCFXt.png)**The moment we realize that as a species, we are so small and insignificant.**
